  <brief_title>Renal Denervation Using the Vessix Renal Denervation System for the Treatment of Hypertension (REDUCE HTN:REINFORCE)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Boston Scientific Clinical Trial of Renal Denervation Using the Vessix Reduce™ Catheter and Vessix™ Generator for the Treatment of HyperTensioN: REINFORCE</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
